Length about 2330; head length 247, width behind eyes 207, po length 85, eye dorsal length 75; median length of pronotum 157, width across ep 332, am 12, aa 50, ml 70, ep 112, pa 117; width of mesonotum 325; fore wing length 1010; tergite IX setae S1 200, S2 215, S3 222; tergite X length 202, basal width 102, apical width 46; length(width) of antennal segments 
<date box="[991,1118,1690,1715]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" value="1965-03" valueMax="1965-08-31" valueMin="1965-03-00">III–VIII 65</date>
(32), 57(31), 60(30), 57(25), 60(20), 35(12), respectively.
</paragraph>
